zkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=a9ab4a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/781</a><br />\n    18區頻道群組 / 分區哨兵<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F782&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e3323dea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/782</a><br />\n     校巴 / 大型哨兵 / 交通消息<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F783&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=6c6a12f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/783</a><br />\n     醫療支援 / 法律支援<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F784&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=7600d302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/784</a><br />\n物資 / 防具 / 助養 / 捐贈 / 支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F785&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=f958fc11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/785</a><br />\n國際 / 文宣 / 學界 / 義教 / 政黨<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F786&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b3c18b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/786</a><br />\n     新聞 / 各式各樣<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F787&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=3c99a476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/787</a><br />\n     黃絲良心商店 / 藍屍罪惡黑店<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F788&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=87140893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/788</a><br />\n     業界同路人 / 工會<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F789&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=084c2780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/789</a><br />\n     黑警 / 罪證 / 藍屍 / 仆街<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hongkongindex/790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex%2F790&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=a2c27c7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hongkongindex/790</a></span><br />\n_________________________________<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">［人最重要，安全第一］［適當時撤退，是高度智慧的表現］</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足，你已經盡力🙏必要時考慮散水🙏Respect🙏<br />\n____________________________<br />\n［撤退手足，棄裝、換衫、扮路人］<br />\n<br />\n如果確定撤退，請你棄gear、換淺色衫。就算比黑警係 車輛 / 行人路 捉左，只要唔好講嘢，佢冇證據根本好難告你。<br />\n<br />\n記住，你係普通路人，你唔係示威者，你出黎食飯行街。<br />\n<br />\n唔使擔心gear，手足之後會夾錢買番比你。<br />\n<br />\n身上冇gear、著淺色衫，黑警根本唔知邊個係示威者，佢高調拉低調放，想嚇9我地。<br />\n____________________________<br />\n［如果比黑警拉，即刻除口罩，大聲狂叫自己既名］［唔可以變成失蹤人口］<br />\n<br />\n比黑警拉果陣，即刻除口罩，大聲狂叫自己既名，比人見到你既樣，比人知道你既名。<br />\n<br />\n叫大聲d，唔好怕醜，咁樣做可以減少你成為失蹤人口既機會。<br />\n____________________________<br />\n［各區手足，緊急支援義士］［快d落街幫手］<br />\n<br />\n各區手足帶幾件淺色衫，立即落街，主動協助義士散水。最好提供暫避地方。功德無量。🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏<br />\n_________________________________<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［狗屋找尋被捕手足］［打電話］［轉載，請廣傳］</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 如果手足係旺角被捕，先打旺角警署，搵唔到就再試油麻地或者深水埗警署，以被捕地點作圓心向外既警署逐間打。<br />\n<br />\n2. 有全名加身份證去問最好，唔係直系親屬可能會拒絕回答。<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔好一次過問成條手足名單，警署可以因為懷疑你想包攬訴訟而拒絕回答，同埋親屬都唔會有一條名單去問。<br />\n<br />\n4. 岩岩被捕有機會冇咁快到警署，被捕後一兩小時打應該穩陣啲。<br />\n<br />\n5. 確認警署好重要！因為律師救人要知道地方先救到。<br />\n<br />\n6. 如果搵左好多間警署都冇人，有機會去左醫院，就可能要聯絡醫院了。"},{"pid":"ef9c04918ab87f492cdfc5185ea041b4b2af6711","tid":1721180,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"5毛唔敢推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8132b9dc8f102f59f5f064b50f5a00b7a1917c","tid":1721180,"uid":156929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c08b19623dec6e6e7b8011be418bc149ff52dd8","tid":1721180,"uid":104928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3430c4283b75ef5a276215a594c1be3a80a486a5","tid":1721180,"uid":119767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:13:25.000Z","msg":"1823問"},{"pid":"bc64b7de3a8c55787f7640d6d42d02ee16291d64","tid":1721180,"uid":227637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2218a233868502ab853ff0703ddab0d27a22bf1c","tid":1721180,"uid":132614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"點解嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b70d087056ad638982de229642838044d78b753","tid":1721180,"uid":272424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a74919ce961a14801db71dc06cc6f42d91f73b","tid":1721180,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3430c4283b75ef5a276215a594c1be3a80a486a5","tid":1721180,"uid":119767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:13:25.000Z","msg":"1823問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}